values: My name is Margaret, I love to read and write. I also like to watch weird movies no one else has seen, like "frequency" and "benny and joon" ( I can't believe that no one i know has seen these movies). I love to eat, which i know isn't healthy, but it's not like I'm fat or anything(not yet anyway). This blog is to pretty much write about me, I don't know who will read this, but I really don't care. So if you are bored and have nothing better to do stop by! Comment if you want me to add you!! Margaret
